nd creative problem-solving to build products that people actually want to use.","bio_personal":"When I'm not pushing pixels, you'll find me brewing specialty coffee, producing music, or contributing to design communities. I love sharing knowledge and learning from other designers.","designer_name":"Alex Morgan","years_experience":2,"projects_completed":50,"happy_clients":20,"email":"alex@example.com","avatar_url":"/uploads/26f36748-cf7d-4e8d-bf77-a34cf772a12d.jpeg","availability_status":"Currently Available","availability_note":"Open for new projects starting February 2026","trusted_companies":["TechCorp","StartupXYZ","DesignLab","InnovateCo"],"location":"San Francisco, CA","skills":["User Research","Wireframing","Prototyping","UI Design","Design Systems","Usability Testing","Information Architecture","Interaction Design"],"hero_heading_prefix":"I design henten","hero_heading_gradient":"meaningful digital","hero_heading_suffix":"experiences"}
